https://circuitverse.org/users/3198/projects/improved-4-bit-ripple-carry-adder-007a445b-1d3c-456a-9634-42080b038184

Sum bit (z)     : z     =  x XOR y  XOR c                 (where c is the carry-in from the previous bit).
Carry-out bit   : c_out = (x AND y) OR ((x XOR y) AND c)